EXPRESSION: COUNTROWS(FILTER('DB Contracts', 'DB Contracts'[Cost_Saving] <> 0)) & " of " & COUNTROWS(FILTER('DB Contracts', 'DB Contracts'[Status] = "Active"))

VAR CurrentMonth = SELECTEDVALUE(Months[_Endofmonthdate])
VAR CurrentContract = SELECTEDVALUE(Combined_Contracts[Contract_Number])
VAR MaxRow =
    CALCULATE (
        MAX (Combined_Contracts[Amendment_Version] ),
        FILTER (
            Combined_Contracts,
            Combined_Contracts[Contract_Number] = CurrentContract &&
            CurrentMonth >= EOMONTH(Combined_Contracts[Contract_Date], 0) &&
            CurrentMonth <= EOMONTH(Combined_Contracts[Expired_Date], 0)
        )
    )
RETURN
IF ( ISBLANK(MaxRow), 0, MaxRow + 1 )

SUMX (
    ADDCOLUMNS (
        SUMMARIZE (Combined_Contracts, Combined_Contracts[Contract_Number]),
        "LatestAmount",
            CALCULATE (
                MAX (Combined_Contracts[Contract_Amount]),
                FILTER (
                    Combined_Contracts,
                    Combined_Contracts[Contract_Number] = EARLIER (Combined_Contracts[Contract_Number]) &&
                    Combined_Contracts[Amendment_Version] =
                        CALCULATE (
                            MAX (Combined_Contracts[Amendment_Version]),
                            FILTER (
                                Combined_Contracts,
                                Combined_Contracts[Contract_Number] = EARLIER (Combined_Contracts[Contract_Number])
                            )
                        )
                )
            )
    ),
    [LatestAmount]
)

VAR CurrentContract = SELECTEDVALUE(Combined_Contracts[Contract_Number])
VAR CurrentVersion = SELECTEDVALUE(Combined_Contracts[Amendment_Version])
VAR MaxVersion =
    CALCULATE (
        MAX (Combined_Contracts[Amendment_Version]),
        FILTER (
            Combined_Contracts,
            Combined_Contracts[Contract_Number] = CurrentContract
        )
    )
RETURN
    IF (
        NOT ISBLANK(CurrentContract) &&
        CurrentVersion = MaxVersion,
        "Yes",
        "No"
    )
